## 🧠 AI Chatbot

This portfolio includes a GPT-powered assistant with selectable personas (Friendly, Sarcastic, Coach, etc). Try it live at:

👉 [Live Demo](https://advanced-ai-portfolio.onrender.com)

Built with FastAPI + OpenAI + Vanilla JS

ai-portfolio/
├── backend/
│   ├── fastapi_app.py       # FastAPI backend
│   └── .env                 # Secrets (not committed to GitHub)
├── public/                  # Frontend assets served via FastAPI
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── style.css
│   └── chatbot.js
├── requirements.txt         # Backend Python dependencies
└── README.md


git clone https://github.com/devjclosterman/advanced-Ai-Portfolio.git
cd advanced-Ai-Portfolio

Create a .env file in the backend/ folder:
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

Install Backend Dependencies: 
cd backend
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate  # On Windows
source venv/bin/activate  # On macOS/Linux

pip install -r ../requirements.txt

Run the app from the root folder: 
uvicorn backend.fastapi_app:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000


Deploying on Render: 
Go to Render.com

Click "New Web Service"

Connect your GitHub repo

Choose the following settings:

Root Directory: ./

Start Command:

bash
Copy
Edit
uvicorn backend.fastapi_app:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
Build Command:

bash
Copy
Edit
pip install -r requirements.txt
Add an Environment Variable:

Key: OPENAI_API_KEY

Value: your-openai-key

Click Deploy

✅ Features
✨ Real-time AI chatbot powered by OpenAI GPT-4o

🌐 FastAPI backend with full CORS support

💅 Fully styled UI with dark theme, personality modes, and animations

🔁 Chat memory & system persona switching

☁️ Live on Render, code managed via GitHub
